{"tid":1630771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（URGENT）大家仲記唔記得四色？","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:58:04.000Z","uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1319dfabaf9fa44bb0e3fa3120d95be969b8a14f","tid":1630771,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"要分清至好裝修！<br />\n已經有人裝修錯中原地產<br />\n係藍係紅都絕對唔係黑！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1630599/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1630599/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"93d7b0e3f1b7f6225a4cb57b3cb27853fcd333ce","tid":1630771,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7246eac1ee3dbd0e834c047f5d386f897ceb3bf9","tid":1630771,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉《裝修佬必讀》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"e96ef2f9055f95abf8c2ee6a18480d5aab9f5fa7","tid":1630771,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"56c3267bddfccae9311e568e90487246f4f26320","tid":1630771,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16bed2095252512cbb3829317bff156b9a4637b0","tid":1630771,"uid":148262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"44908469994dba29c348413f32aa40a7166b6245","tid":1630771,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"aa2ba90f15d0cb5cf4ea64a98042e9e9f9776cd4","tid":1630771,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"88b5d45af112ef70cf08677a595530897a65aef7","tid":1630771,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"係POPO卧底做嘅<br />\n意在抹黑示威者<br />\nspread開去"},{"pid":"5996015c94446891a990e94c0b7b82382026bfaa","tid":1630771,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad50cdd74404f222e995f24d150c7cde9e3a28c5","tid":1630771,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"a7debfb38f7869f52f9d594e9c4585e16d347f41","tid":1630771,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"<em